{
  "stem": "4289.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we, Germany to Brazil, she wanted me to join her family to be with her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I did write her unhappy letters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was supposed to organize some kind of a help in Vienna, where Jews went through the transport, from Poland went through Vienna, that her friends will pick me up.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she'll have ready passport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all that was arranged in a very hectic way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father and my stepmother finally were planning that I will run away from the train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my stepmother was really happy about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She'd finally get rid of me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When I came to Vienna, I did go out from the other side of the train station through a window.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was looking for the people who came to claim me there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a, a son who was married and a partner to the business of my aunt in Brazil.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were the parents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they told me very bad news, that I don't have any passport.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have no papers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And unfortunately, I'll have to go back to the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "While I was away, the whole day with those people, the head of the Sochnut who had all the passports was looking for me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the train was stopped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People did not-- were not able to continue their trip to Italy, where a boat would take us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was very angry with my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He found out who was missing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they count the heads.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the evening when I came back, the man was so angry that he almost cursed my father.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he really gave him a curse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, after this terrible times, you finally found your daughter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you're giving her away?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For what?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
